1. Prerequisites

 - Visual Studio 2022
 - pandas Python library
 - matplotlib Python library
 - tkinter Python library
 - employee.py class library for the first app
 - data.CSV file for the second app

2. Run

Usage:
   - python.exe 1.py
   - python.exe 2.py

